.TH MNEMOSYNE-SERVE-START 1 "2026-06-23" "mnemosyne" "Mnemosyne CLI"
.SH NAME
mnemosyne serve-start \- Start a local HTTP API server (stdlib http.server, no external dependencies).
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmnemosyne serve-start\fR [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Start a local HTTP API server (stdlib http.server, no external dependencies).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-host\fR
Bind address (default: 127.0.0.1)
.TP
\fB\-\-port\fR
Listen port (default: 57832)
.TP
\fB\-\-db\-path\fR
Knowledge graph database path
.SH SEE ALSO
mnemosyne(1)
